# Keeps the Docker build context (repo root) small and fast, and is
# defense-in-depth against ever accidentally baking secrets/venvs into an
# image even if a Dockerfile's COPY commands get broadened later.
.git
.env
**/venv
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
**/data
docs/mockups/*.png
pi_client/waveshare_epd
